---
alwaysApply: true
---

Every privileged action requires a capability check.

Use nonces for state-changing admin requests.

Validate first, sanitize when needed, escape on output.

Never expose secrets client-side.

Never log or transmit secrets, tokens, passwords, or raw API keys.

For outbound reporting, minimize payloads, document fields, and log delivery outcomes.

Any personal data handling must consider export/erase integration and privacy disclosure.
